{"build_type":"library","description":"Step-4 child worker. Spawned with a context whose slot 4 holds this thread's own FS block. Sets FS to that block, initializes its OWN thread-local arena (tls_cursor=5000, tls_end=6000), does two bump allocations (expect 5000, 5016), then stores its results c1,c2,final-cursor,final-end into the block at slots 3..6 (beyond the 0/8/16 thread-local slots) so the parent can read them, and returns 99 (trampoline delivers to context[0], rings the doorbell). Proves the child's arena lives entirely in its own block.","module_name":"set-thread-pointer-then-bump-arena-storing-results","package_name":"set-thread-pointer-then-bump-arena-storing-results","function_definitions":{"set-thread-pointer-then-bump-arena-storing-results":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"context","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"three","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":3},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"four","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"five","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"six","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":6},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"set_fs","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":4098},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"v5000","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":5000},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"v6000","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal"